content:
Kai Deng is a master candidate in DSP-Group, Special technical research center, Institute of Computing Technology, Chinese Academy of Sciences, advised by Prof. Ping Yao. He worked as the Embedded Computation Group Leader of Amaze Group (2017~2019) .
His research interests lie within deep learning for Computer Vision, particularly in generative adversarial nets and object detection. His is also involved in remote sensing area and its application.
